Spain's consumer price index rose 0.6pct in March after a 0.4 pct increase in February and 0.3 pctin March last year, the National Statistics Institute said.    The March rise brought the year on year rate to 6.3 pct.The government has set a five pct target for 1987 consumerprice inflation after an 8.3 pct increase last year. REUTER&#3;